### Useful resources

- [How to Build a Responsive Navigation Bar with a Dropdown Menu using JavaScript](https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/how-to-build-a-responsive-navigation-bar-with-dropdown-menu-using-javascript/) - This helped me for development of the dropdown navigation bar. Navigation bars are essential components used a lot in websites and web apps

